---
import OldWebLayout from '@/layouts/OldWebLayout.astro';
---
<OldWebLayout title="House Rules" section="houserules">
  <h1>House Rules</h1>
  <ol class="old-shell old-body" style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.7;">
    <li>House rules apply.</li>
    <li>No soft hands.</li>
    <li>Call your own fouls.</li>
    <li>Scratch on the break equals re-rack.</li>
    <li>Three fouls equals loss of game.</li>
    <li>No coaching unless we like you.</li>
    <li>Respect the table, the players and the room.</li>
    <li>Management decision is final.</li>
    <li>If you argue a call, we laugh.</li>
    <li>Tip the bartender.</li>
    <li>Don’t be an ass.</li>
  </ol>
</OldWebLayout>
